

I recommend making symbolic links for the input and output, to make it very clear what is what. 
For example, symlinking to the input files:

   $ ln -s /glade/work/lvank/from_cartesius/b.e21.BHIST.f09_g17.CMIP6-historical.003b/vector2gridded3d input

and the output files:

   $ mkdir /glade/work/lvank/from_cartesius/b.e21.BHIST.f09_g17.CMIP6-historical.003b/DstGrid3d
   $ ln -s /glade/work/lvank/from_cartesius/b.e21.BHIST.f09_g17.CMIP6-historical.003b/DstGrid3d output

